Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:50.88,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Come on tell me why we are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:53.72,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}This endless bloody war
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:56.08,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Why I'm crying in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:59.21,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}You guys are not little boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:02.72,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Just stop what you're doing for me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.54,0:24:05.48,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}It's not really good for you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.48,0:24:08.18,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We should know where we're goin?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.18,0:24:10.38,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nobody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:13.14,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Fly high
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.14,0:24:16.46,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}How we got lost in here
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.92,0:24:22.08,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Bullets pour like rain
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.78,0:24:26.55,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Our chances like shooting stars
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.81,0:24:29.47,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}You can hear something in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.47,0:24:34.34,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Everything is linked around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.74,0:24:39.89,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Break your door to get out the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.12,0:24:41.62,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Face reality
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.62,0:24:46.30,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}You can hear my heart say only one
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.59,0:24:49.96,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}It always feels so good
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.96,0:24:53.77,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}It's so good for me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.77,0:24:56.61,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Every hope around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.83,0:25:00.16,OPEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Take my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.64,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Unknown soldier lying on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:26.97,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Explosions forever
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:30.61,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Now you take me away from danger
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:34.49,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}We had always covered up your face
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:37.09,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Out there who will watch your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:41.01,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Because I don't know if I can stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.69,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Game over
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:46.02,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Now we hate our brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:49.88,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}No longer can move my feet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:50.58,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}But it's
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.32,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Keep on keeping on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:54.60,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}And it's I just wanna know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:57.35,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Inside it's I don't want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:14:00.77,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Over head they fly high it's going
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.43,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}On and on and on
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:07.53,INEN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Will we oversee the smile of love and peace for everyone?
